  "body": "Hello,\nI just noticed that there are 3 bacteria have this term, which is being given by PANTHER;\nGO:0070478 nuclear-transcribed mRNA catabolic process, 3'-5' exonucleolytic nonsense-mediated decay\nAs bacteria do not have nuclei, nor NMD, this term makes no sense. \n\nCan you add the following please? Any other terms related to non-mediated RNA decay should also have this constraint.\nnever in taxon: 2\n\nThanks, Andrea\n",
